---
title: Easy Asian Sweet Soy Prawn Bowl with Butter Rice, Honey-Soy Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: Sweet soy prawn is the star in this Asian-inspired bowl. Paired with honey-soy veggies, this dish is bound to satisfy both your salty and sweet cravings! Topped off with a creamy sesame dressing and crispy shallots, we hope you're as excited about this dish as we are.

